N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 3 ยง 4.3 - Existence of public accommodation office not considered in evaluating application for full-service branch

State Regulations

The existence of a public accommodation office shall not be
considered as a factor in the evaluation of an application for a full-service
branch. Notes
